org.drools.planner.examples.ras2012.model

Class Arc

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drools.planner.examples.ras2012.model.Section
      • org.drools.planner.examples.ras2012.model.Arc

  • public class Arc
extends Section
    The arc represents a single length of railroad track, whose properties such as maximum speed are uniform all over it. Route consist solely of arcs, each arc has the west and the east Node.
